<div class="msg">
    <div class="weui_msg">
        <div class="weui_icon_area"><i class="weui_icon_info weui_icon_msg"></i></div>
        <div class="weui_text_area">
            <h2 class="weui_msg_title">拨打电话或短信</h2>
            <p class="weui_msg_desc">如果你能确认自己什么时候有空，可以直接短信通知客人来看病，否则就拨打电话先沟通一下吧, 然后再送短信通知</p>
        </div>
        <div class="weui_opr_area">
            <p class="weui_btn_area">
                <a href="<%= claim_reservation_path(@reservation) %>" class="weui_btn weui_btn_primary">发送短信</a>
                <a href="javascript: IM.call(<%= current_user.doctor.id %>, <%= @reservation.user_a %>, <%= @reservation.id %>, <%= @reservation.mobile_phone %>);" class="weui_btn weui_btn_default">拨打电话</a>
            </p>
        </div>
        <div class="weui_extra_area">
            <a href="">查看帮助</a>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
